+ *
+ * Prerequisites:
+ *   - STRIPE_PRIVATE_KEY must be set (use test mode key)
+ *   - STRIPE_ORG_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID or STRIPE_TEAM_MONTHLY_PRICE_ID should be set
